How to generate certificate for user.
=====================================
1. Generate private key for manish user. 
root@kube-master:~/cert# openssl genrsa -out manish.key 2048

2. Generate CSR for manish user. 
root@kube-master:~/cert# openssl req -new -key manish.key -subj "/CN=manish/O=qaengineer" -out manish.csr

3. 
root@kube-master:~/cert# openssl x509 -req -in manish.csr -CA ca.crt -CAkey ca.key -CAcreateserial -out manish.crt -days 365
Signature ok
subject=CN = manish, O = qaengineer
